# Import Center Rule

## Source Of Truth
- If this file conflicts with [CLAUDE.md](../../CLAUDE.md), **CLAUDE.md wins**.

## Workflow Priority
1. Excel import
2. Manual entry
3. PDF/scan attachment registration
4. Legacy contract data registration

## Required Flow
`job created -> mapped -> validated -> fix -> completed`

## Required Artifacts
- Original source file record (or source metadata)
- Mapping state
- Validation issues
- Fix path (direct action/route)
- Job history/audit trail

## Current Strategy
- Support "upload + manual mapping + correction" first.
- Do not block delivery on full automation/OCR.

